'''克卜勒452(英語: Kepler-452)'''（開普勒） 是一顆距離地球1,400光年的[[G型主序星|G型主序星]]，在天球上位於天鵝座。<ref name="Witze">{{cite news|last1 = Witze|first1 = Alexandra|title = NASA spies Earth-sized exoplanet orbiting Sun-like star|url = http://www.nature.com/news/nasa-spies-earth-sized-exoplanet-orbiting-sun-like-star-1.18048|accessdate = 23 July 2015|work = Nature|date = July 23, 2015|archive-date = 2015-07-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150725212759/http://www.nature.com/news/nasa-spies-earth-sized-exoplanet-orbiting-sun-like-star-1.18048|dead-url = no}}</ref> 它與[[太阳|太陽]]的溫度相似，亮度比太陽多了20%，質量多了4%，半徑多了10%。<ref>{{cite news|last1 = Chou|first1 = Felicia|last2 = Johnson|first2 = Michelle|title = NASA’s Kepler Mission Discovers Bigger, Older Cousin to Earth|url = http://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-kepler-mission-discovers-bigger-older-cousin-to-earth|accessdate = 23 July 2015|agency = NASA|date = July 23, 2015|archive-date = 2015-10-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151007035447/http://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-kepler-mission-discovers-bigger-older-cousin-to-earth/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1 = Rincon|first1 = Paul|title = 'Earth 2.0' found in Nasa Kepler telescope haul|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-33641648|publisher = [[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate = 23 July 2015|date = July 23, 2015|archive-date = 2015-07-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150723191144/http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-33641648|dead-url = no}}</ref> 年齡約有60億年，比太陽古老15億年。

系外行星[[克卜勒452b|克卜勒452b]]（開普勒）的軌道位於克卜勒452的適居帶之間，在2015年7月由克卜勒太空望遠鏡發現。（開普勒太空望遠鏡）

==行星系統==
它至少有一個被證實的[[太陽系外行星|系外行星]]、[[克卜勒452b|克卜勒452b]]，由[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]2015年7月發現的。

